"upload_disclaimer.body.policy_link":"aizliegtas izmanto\u0161anas politika","upload_disclaimer.body.suffix":".",disclaimer:"Pomelli var pie\u013caut k\u013c\u016bdas, t\u0101p\u0113c r\u016bp\u012bgi p\u0101rbaudiet t\u0101 sniegto inform\u0101ciju.","disclaimer.professional":"\u0122ener\u0113tie izvades dati ir tikai informat\u012bvi un neaizst\u0101j profesion\u0101las juridisk\u0101s, m\u0101rketinga vai uz\u0146\u0113m\u0113jdarb\u012bbas konsult\u0101cijas.",sample_businesses:"\u0160ie ir m\u0101ksl\u012bg\u0101 intelekta \u0123ener\u0113ti uz\u0146\u0113mumu paraugi ar visp\u0101r\u012bgiem izdom\u0101tiem uz\u0146\u0113mumu nosaukumiem. J\u016bs esat atbild\u012bgs par jebk\u0101du gala datu precizit\u0101tes un likum\u012bbas p\u0101rbaudi.",
"settings.help_title":"Pal\u012bdziet uzlabot Pomelli pakalpojumu ikvienam","settings.help_on":"At\u013caujiet izmantot j\u016bsu datus (tostarp j\u016bsu uz\u0146\u0113muma DNS un kampa\u0146u datus), lai apm\u0101c\u012btu Google \u0123enerat\u012bv\u0101 MI mode\u013cus, t\u0101d\u0113j\u0101di pal\u012bdzot uzlabot Pomelli pakalpojumu gan jums, gan citiem t\u0101 lietot\u0101jiem. M\u0113s veicam darb\u012bbas, lai aizsarg\u0101tu j\u016bsu konfidencialit\u0101ti.","settings.learn_more":"Uzziniet vair\u0101k",
"settings.help_on_tail":"Ja \u0161is iestat\u012bjums ir izsl\u0113gts, j\u016bsu dati joproj\u0101m var tikt izmantoti, lai sekm\u012bg\u0101k atkl\u0101tu kr\u0101p\u0161anu, \u013caunpr\u0101t\u012bgu izmanto\u0161anu un","settings.help_off":"J\u016bsu turpm\u0101kie dati netiks izmantoti Google \u0123enerat\u012bvo MI mode\u013cu uzlabo\u0161anai, iz\u0146emot gad\u012bjumus, kad nos\u016bt\u012bsiet atsauksmes. Anonimiz\u0113ti paraugi, ko jau p\u0101rbaud\u012bju\u0161i p\u0101rskat\u012bt\u0101ji, tiek saglab\u0101ti l\u012bdz trim gadiem, pat ja tos izdz\u0113\u0161at.",
"settings.help_off_tail":"Ja \u0161is iestat\u012bjums ir izsl\u0113gts, j\u016bsu dati joproj\u0101m var tikt izmantoti, lai sekm\u012bg\u0101k atkl\u0101tu kr\u0101p\u0161anu, \u013caunpr\u0101t\u012bgu izmanto\u0161anu un","privacy.google_tos":"Google pakalpojumu snieg\u0161anas noteikumu","privacy.prohibited_policy":"aizliegtas izmanto\u0161anas politikas p\u0101rk\u0101pumus un rea\u0123\u0113tu uz tiem","tos.and":"un","settings.title":"Konta iestat\u012bjumi","settings.subtitle":"Skatiet un redi\u0123\u0113jiet sava konta iestat\u012bjumus",
